{"tid":1573022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【極緊要，幫推上頂】美國左派選民反對民主人權法!!!","createTime":"2019-09-16T00:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:04:09.000Z","uid":274747,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbc318e19f6320d71ce030faf217ee2d065dda4","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"我知道大家舉美國旗係為左討好美國人，<br />\n但自從有美國國旗出現係香港示威之後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">左派議員不斷收到美國選民要求佢哋停止支持香港</span></span></strong>。<br />\n我認識幾個過去幾年暗地裏係美國政界，一路幫大家推動呢個人權民主法既朋友，<br />\n佢哋都confirm左有左派議員已經動搖緊，有可能過唔到。<br />\n大家要明白，對美國人黎講，人權民主法並無任何國家利益，<br />\n佢哋只係一個政治上既表態，就算條法案通過左，都要隔一段時間finalize到個制裁名單，<br />\n然後先會去到真正制裁。呢個時間係非常冗長，美國人通唔通過其實無咩所謂，只係呢張係一張要脅到中國既牌。<br />\n而而家如果根據消息同埋新聞，如果貿易談判香港真係唔再係一個考慮，咁人權民主法好可能會無左。<br />\n<br />\n大選當前，舉美國旗或者會令擁抱「世界警察」既右派選民同政客感覺良好。<br />\n但如果我地要贏呢場仗，我地唔單止要贏一部分，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要巴結到所有議員包括某啲人最討厭既左膠。</span><br />\n麻煩大家幫忙spread開去，而家我地唔需要舉美國旗，<br />\n而係係twitter全面打英文輿論戰，令美國人知道我地正面對一場人道災難。"},{"pid":"8e8c1a667e2086631d63bb3caa52aa03a9de23fc","tid":1573022,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:21:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5310dd725abc28d2ea8fa7e7bbcbd66c82027c4","tid":1573022,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"shit!"},{"pid":"5bda78f48fb77fef0723be648458094e8eba57f3","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:22:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8da35e45455333ba2c15a7e8887cba84b93365e","tid":1573022,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:22:45.000Z","msg":"奴隸討好主人"},{"pid":"3078e07225708d5a6a11e4f5abe7f8e4f6be44a3","tid":1573022,"uid":60092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:23:10.000Z","msg":"咁取消關係法囉，教佢哋封後門。"},{"pid":"f3168917e62125f87378a974df97f0768d7dd068","tid":1573022,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31556198f480a93904a9848855f55581b172cd3f","tid":1573022,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:23:57.000Z","msg":"但點解新疆過到？"},{"pid":"5fda38b86b4f459d35b4bc3cf6de0a52971289ae","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3078e07225708d5a6a11e4f5abe7f8e4f6be44a3","tid":1573022,"uid":60092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:23:10.000Z","msg":"咁取消關係法囉，教佢哋封後門。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:27:46.000Z","msg":"取消關係法係貿易談判既最後一張牌，取消之前美國都要安頓好所有外資先，如果唔係，商界反彈，推動取消關係法嗰個大選就玩完。所以你見到過去幾個星期關係法根本唔係無乜提及。<br />\n<br />\n而人權民主法一樣，而家講到明香港唔係貿易談判考慮，如果再無美國民意基礎，條法案好難得到大多數議員支持。<br />\n<br />\n要巴結左膠，一定係要frame做人道災難，專注警察濫捕。"},{"pid":"2e2f4b16f1f8c4cb93d4d768b66cba628553f110","tid":1573022,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31556198f480a93904a9848855f55581b172cd3f","tid":1573022,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:23:57.000Z","msg":"但點解新疆過到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"not done yet as well"},{"pid":"de584432396e7bdb4a6273e951e5dcd07434922c","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31556198f480a93904a9848855f55581b172cd3f","tid":1573022,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:23:57.000Z","msg":"但點解新疆過到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:34:29.000Z","msg":"新疆條法案係美國好多年，<br />\n表態支持既議員數目係明顯多過香港，<br />\n而新疆發生既問題，係美國係好震撼，<br />\n香港當然都係，但今日外媒報導舉美國旗既新聞，<br />\n好多左派真係覺得好唔鍾意。<br />\n我知道香港朋友未必明白，但對左派黎講，民族主義唔係佢地推崇既，美國國旗係令佢地覺得被擺上枱，成為對抗中國既手法。<br />\n我知道大家會問，反共有咩問題，無錯，係無問題，但呢個只係右派理念上會支持大家既原因。實際上，有咩利益呢？其實就只係一張要脅中國既牌，而家舉美國旗，令佢地覺得令貿易談判增加變數，一旦影響到佢地利益，就會即刻縮。<br />\n<br />\n而家貿易談判進度良好，又一次出現G20既情況，香港變成一張暫時放埋一邊既牌。如果我地唔強調人權問題，事實上，從利益上，美國係唔需要支持我地。"},{"pid":"d671301b900a57e259566cef0a9d6735268727d6","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cbdab6a2c12f91b2e6c9f8b4f945f06b7154e50","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:36:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a1f6b508580e26999e7917c4934e7f8a20f7c7f","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:37:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e1a0900fc39415bb54edf509e66f44d75550dff","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"073c047c33c44d1bf5b7f99cc5cc457b9e0d4502","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ada7e3d12caf878c17ad658b9ed9f74161c5ae4","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:39:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3077370632f8f5ec4689ae9c0e03063354cfc18","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3081347a839369599721d18b504dd7739f2513c","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:41:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d25a666054a12eeaa6241bb08b55567e7136ab1e","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f08218fa4cacc9c902330f93a727d7b808ade46a","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:42:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9ab3235130bfedf8380f1fdd8fb400beb12e88f","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:43:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8f4cdd6810159d87b9a222d5b10c3ee046cc57a","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1faa6d462ee219b90d4c7e004b37bff04d3ac0d","tid":1573022,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06611681859f5991e85de2f0d0090152a1d4daad","tid":1573022,"uid":33459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}